cc:Work.dc:title: Le Ice Cube
cc:Work.dc:description: A simple ice cube, perfect for drinks etc. I selected only one ice cube, cleaned it up with The Gimp, and Traced it with Inkscape. You can duplicate it and rotate it to give a more random appearance. Original Public Domain image used can be found at http://www.publicdomainpictures.net/view-image.php?image=15694&picture=ice-cubes
